Information Amplification Chinese Coded Character Set
1 This document specifies the hexadecimal representation of Chinese graphic characters and very binary encodings for information technology.
This document applies to the processing, exchange, storage, transmission, display, input and output of Chinese and other text graphic character information.
This document applies to technical products with information processing and exchange functions for Chinese and other text and graphic characters, including but not limited to input methods, optical character recognition (OCR), editing, proofreading, computer translation, speech synthesis, text transcription, Qiao Neng writing and other software products, as well as computers, communication terminal equipment, e-book reading Yi, learning machines and other portable products.
