The first batch of personal pension financial products on sale can be held for a minimum of 360 days-CNN
The first personal pension financial products go on sale
Home organization of 7 products to choose from Minimum can only be held for 360 days
Personal pension financial products are finally online.
On February 10, China Financial Management released the first batch of personal pension financial management products list, ICBC Financial Management, Agricultural Bank Financial Management and China Post Financial Management seven personal pension financial management products officially sold.
So far, the "shelf" of personal pension accounts has finally gathered four types of products: personal pension savings, personal pension financial management, personal pension insurance, and personal pension public offering funds.
According to reports, the first batch of personal pension financial products, all for public equity open-ended products, including 5 new products, 2 survival products, in addition to 1 product for mixed products, the remaining 6 products are fixed income products.
Beijing Youth Daily reporter saw that four of the five new products from ICBC Financial Management, all fixed income products, the minimum holding period is 365 days, 540 days, 720 days and 1080 days, the corresponding performance comparison benchmarks (annualized) are 3.70%-4.20%, 4.10%-4.60%, 4.40%-4.90%, 5.25%-5.75%.
The remaining new product is "Postbank Wealth Tim Yi Hongjin shortest holding 1095 days No. 1", is also a fixed income product, February 10 began to raise, February 19 ended to raise, risk level II.
Among the two surviving products, one is the Agricultural Bank of China financial management "Agricultural Bank of China concentric and dynamic" 360-day scientific and technological innovation RMB financial management products, the investment nature is mixed class, the risk level is three.
Another surviving product is "Postbank Wealth Tim Yi Hongjin Minimum Hold 365 Days No. 1", a fixed income type, which began to be raised on December 30 last year, officially operated on January 4 this year, and had a cumulative net worth of 1.0011 on February 8.
According to the Opinions of the General Office of the State Council on Promoting the Development of Individual Pensions, the financial products in which funds from individual pension fund accounts can be invested include banking, savings deposits, commercial endowment insurance, and public offering funds.
The first batch of personal pension financial products were released, marking that personal pension investors can officially purchase financial products through personal pension fund accounts.
Last November, the CBRC formulated the Interim Measures for the Administration of Personal Pension Business of Commercial Banks and Wealth Management Companies.
The Measures stipulate that participants may purchase personal pension products such as personal pension savings, personal pension financial management products, personal pension insurance products and personal pension public offering fund products through personal pension fund accounts.
Subsequently, the Ministry of Human Rights and Social Affairs, the Ministry of Finance and the State Administration of Taxation issued a notice clarifying that the personal pension system will be implemented in 36 pioneer cities and regions, including Beijing and Tianjin, as well as Shijiazhuang and Xiong'an New Districts in Hebei Province and Jincheng City in Shanxi Province.
By the end of 2022, there were 19.5 million participants in personal pensions and 6.13 million contributors, with a total contribution amount of 14.2 billion yuan.
Previously, the banks participating in the pilot only listed three types of products: personal pension savings, personal pension insurance products and personal pension public offering funds.
Now that personal pension financial products have come together, how should investors choose?
Experts from the R&D Department of Financial Products of the Bank of Communications said that compared with other personal pension products, the pension financial products and personal pension financial products in the pilot phase have three characteristics.
First, the robustness, risk management mechanism is more sound, investment strategy and philosophy is more robust, and the implementation of non-parent third-party independent custody.
Second, long-term, the duration of pension financial products in the pilot phase are 5 years or more, the next issue of personal pension financial products, the minimum holding period is in principle 1 year, encourage holding more than 3 years.
Third, inclusiveness, product purchase threshold is low, the starting point is generally 1 yuan, some as low as 0.01 yuan, product hosting fees, management fees and other rates are more favorable.
Professionals point out that investors should choose according to product characteristics and their own risk tolerance.
Personal pension savings have a long term, high interest rate, high security characteristics, suitable for people with weak risk tolerance; personal pension insurance products focus on protection, more suitable for people who can not bear investment risk, can accept stable income; while personal pension financial products and public fund products do not protect the capital or income, there is a certain investment risk, but the expected income is higher, suitable for people with a certain financial knowledge, high risk-bearing ability.
