China's e-commerce industry emerges "new variables" , with goods how to do "content is king"?
- China News Service
China News Service, February 11 /PRNewswire-USNewswire/ -- The emergence of "new variables" in China's e-commerce industry, how to do "content is king"?
China-Singapore Business Journalist Xia Bin
“We entered e-commerce late, but from the beginning we realized that content was important to stand out from the millions of stores.
Fang Fang, a "post-90s" girl from Guangdong, now runs a tonic food store on twitter, allowing an offline store with a history of more than 30 years to "blossom" online.
Imitating the tone of old Hong Kong films, with classic Cantonese songs, open @ Fangfang one-person food twitter account, beautiful video is refreshing.
In the recently held twitter e-commerce "looking for peers · quality content sharing session", Fangfang as a representative of quality creators to speak on the scene, introduced the daily creation experience and experience.
She said at the scene: "The well-polished video has gained a lot of attention from netizens, a lot of people are interested in my ingredients, want to follow along with the food, the market opened up all of a sudden.
”
Fangfang relied on the soup video to make more people fall in love with the "taste of Laoguang", and a live broadcast sold up to 300,000 pieces of nourishing ingredients, saving her family's old shop from the brink of collapse.
"No content, no e-commerce" , with the continuous development of short video and live e-commerce, people's e-commerce content requirements and standards are entering a new stage.
At the beginning of the development of live streaming, the studio often used low-cost discounts to attract users, the price advantage seemed to be the only selling point at the time.
In recent years, there are Liu Xihong, Oriental selection and other phenomena such as big V, but also in the vertical segmentation of the emergence of many people and businesses not known to the public, they continue to create quality content in line with their own brand tone, improve long-term business benefits.
Gao Yaxuan, head of the star author operation of twitter e-commerce, said that 6.27 million creators have monetized their content through twitter e-commerce in the past year, and their content creation volume has increased by 252%, and the total turnover has more than doubled.
"Behind these numbers, we can feel a thriving, vibrant ecology of authors.
" said Gao Yaxuan.
The Communication Innovation and Future Media Experimental Platform of Beijing Normal University previously released the E-commerce Industry Content Ecological Health Index (ECHI) Report, which analyzes the importance of quality content, a "new variable" in the current e-commerce industry, from the data dimension, and uses the index to evaluate the content ecology of 27 mainstream e-commerce platforms in China.
According to the above-mentioned report of the e-commerce industry content ecological health index ranking, twitter e-commerce, fast hand, Taobao, Pinduoduo, JD.com in the top five.
According to the report, the content ecology of the e-commerce industry is a comprehensive concept, is the integration of e-commerce and content, but not all content can be integrated with e-commerce, good PGC (professionally produced content) and UGC (user-original content) is a high-quality carrier for integration with e-commerce, the higher the value of the content platform, the richer the consumption and promotion scenarios, the higher the possibility of e-commerce implantation, the stronger the commercial value, the higher the proportion of e-commerce content production and content consumption that is gradually integrated and distributed in the public and private spheres.
At the scene, Yu Guoming, a professor at the School of Journalism and Communication of Beijing Normal University and chairman of the China Media Economics and Management Professional Committee, made an analysis and interpretation of the Report.
He said that in terms of content value, the current e-commerce industry has transitioned from "consumption accessibility" to "consumption quality" stage, high-quality, professional, differentiated content is the "hard currency" of the e-commerce industry.
At the same time, content has become the foundation and grasp of the new stage of e-commerce development, knowledge payment, professional knowledge, KOL (key opinion leader) and other PGC content began to become standard in e-commerce live broadcast.
Looking forward to the future development of the e-commerce industry, Yu Guoming put forward two suggestions.
One is to promote the overall improvement of the ecological health and quality of e-commerce content from the perspective of improving the content structure, to create positive content creation and management standards, and to achieve the index and dynamic balance of the content ecological health system in the e-commerce industry.
Another is from the external ecological point of view, to achieve the healthy development of the content e-commerce industry and the value of the external environment synergy and co-creation.
"The future e-commerce industry also needs more data, artificial intelligence support, to form a forecast of future development stability; in addition, to provide businesses with more standardized, healthy growth space, to achieve the value of enterprises, users, products and services in the e-commerce industry synergy, to create a healthy content ecosystem.
